name: bmalhotra03/Hadoop-Product-Review-Analyzer
description: Developed a Hadoop MapReduce application to analyze product reviews by calculating the total number of reviews and the average rating for each product. The application utilizes custom mappers and reducers to process the data and generate insights into product performance based on user ratings.

name: bmalhotra03/Hadoop-Inverted-Index-Builder
description: Developed a Hadoop MapReduce application to construct an inverted index from text data. The application extracts words from documents, tracks their locations, and builds a reverse index mapping each word to the files and positions where they appear.

name: bmalhotra03/Hadoop-Log-Month-Processor
description: Developed a Hadoop MapReduce application to process web server logs, extracting and partitioning data by month. The project includes custom mappers, reducers, and a partitioner to efficiently distribute log entries across 12 reducers, one for each month, and count occurrences based on log entry IP addresses.

name: bmalhotra03/Hadoop-Average-Word-Length
description: Implemented a Hadoop MapReduce application to calculate the average length of words grouped by their initial letter. The project utilizes a custom mapper to extract the first letter of each word and its length, and a reducer to compute the average word length for each letter.
